import React from 'react'; import PropTypes from 'prop-types'; import { Link, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; export default function Navbar(props, isLog) { const navigate = useNavigate(); if (!isLog) { document.getElementById("Home").tagName = "p"; } return (
); } Navbar.propTypes = { title: PropTypes.string.isRequired, about: PropTypes.string.isRequired, }; Navbar.defaultProps = { title: "set title here", about: "About ", };
